title: AWAITS cross-products
pid: c43bd731-ffba-4f77-bf40-2257197b0adb
body: |2-
  where I wrote [[id:e054463e-277c-4283-932c-cb40f26f7f45][? art | example \\ irony]]
  it might have been nice to be able to put
  irony in a cross-product producing bracketed list:
  { '? art' | example' } \\ {irony | something else}
  would create four paths
  (where "x/y" is "x contains y")
  - irony / ?art
  - irony / example
  - something else / ?art
  - something else / example
